yum install httpd elinks	      Install Apache Web Server and Elinks (text based browser)
cd /var/www/html	              Location of files for the Apache Web Server


• vim /var/www/html/index.html	      Create a page with "Welcome to my webserver"; Restart httpd service and then visualize the content via elinks on the localhost server
 
Welcome to my webserver
 
• systemctl restart httpd
• elinks httpd://localhost


elinks httpd http://localhost	       Verify Web Server connection


cd /etc/httpd/conf	               Configuration for the Apache Web Server. Document Root shows where the Apache will look for its document.
ls
vim httpd.conf
